    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "ハァッ……ハァッ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*huff* *huff*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "大分、いい感じになってきたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s looking pretty good‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まだ全体的にメリハリが甘い所があるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But as a whole‚ you’re still lacking in dynamics.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "動きを合わせるのは大事だけど、それで動きが曖昧に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moving in unison is essential‚ of course‚ but if your unison muddies your movements‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なっては、逆に格好悪く見えるから注意するように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "that can actually make your dancing look dull‚ so be careful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.266666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（一流の先生が特別に見てくれることになって良かった）\n（まさか琴乃達の歌を聴いて、見てくれるなんてな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I’m glad we got a first-rate coach to give them some special lessons.)\n(I can’t believe she decided to help them after seeing them sing.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "じゃあ、次のフォーメーションに移ります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ let’s go into the next formation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "各自、自分が立つ位置は確認出来てる？　言ってみて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you all know where your marks are? Tell me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.466666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "0番から5番です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Position 0 to position 5.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "3番から2番に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Position 3 to position 2.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "4番から6番です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Position 4 to position 6.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "え、ええと……渚と逆でしたわよね……\nだから、6番から4番！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ uh‚ I was the opposite of Nagisa‚ correct?\nSo‚ position 6 to position 4!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "ここから、そっち",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I go from here… to there!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "番号ですわよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We need numbers‚ you know!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、先生\n細かい所まで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your help‚ coach.\nYou’ve been so thorough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いいえ。可能性のある子達を見るのは楽しいから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My pleasure. I enjoy teaching girls who have potential.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "むしろ、お礼を言うのは私の方よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I should actually be thanking you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "……いたっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ouch!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣。間違っていますわよ\n大丈夫かしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei‚ that was the wrong move.\nAre you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……じゃあ、俺はさくら達の方を\n見に行ってきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going to go check up\non Sakura’s group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（芽衣、言いたいことは分かってる）\n（……でも、今は練習に集中してくれ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Mei‚ I know what you want to say.)\n(But please‚ focus on rehearsals for now.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 88.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
