      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 88.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ hi‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。休憩中？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey. Are you on a break?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 94.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "はい。先生にも練習のし過ぎは怪我の元だから\n気を付けるようにって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. The coach says overwork causes injuries.\nSo we should be careful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……歌はどう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How’s your singing coming along?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 102
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "自信もあるけど、不安もあります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel confident… but I also feel anxious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、自分達で作った歌だから、うまくいかなくても\nこれなら諦めが付くって、みんな言ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Still‚ since it’s a song we composed ourselves‚ even if it doesn’t go well‚\nwe’ll be able to accept defeat. Everyone’s said so.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 112.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_18_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈の歌声を卒業すると、さくら達サニーピースは）\n（自分達で歌詞を作った）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(After saying goodbye to Mana’s voice‚ Sakura and Sunny Peace)\n(have written their own song lyrics.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
